ED_DecisionText:
At its 51st plenary meeting, on 5 December 2016, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the First Committee,43 recalling its resolutions 54/54 F of 1 December 1999, 55/33 A of 20 November 2000, 56/24 B of 29 November 2001, 57/71 of 22 November 2002, 58/37 of 8 December 2003, 59/67 of 3 December 2004, 61/59 of 6 December 2006 and 63/55 of 2 December 2008 and its decisions 60/515 of 8 December 2005, 62/514 of 5 December 2007, 65/517 of 8 December 2010, 66/516 of 2 December 2011, 67/516 of 3 December 2012, 68/517 of 5 December 2013 and 69/517 of 2 December 2014, decided to include in the provisional agenda of its seventy-third session the item entitled “Missiles”.

(See A/71/450, para 113, draft decion II; A/71/PV.51)
